---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Refund & Transfer Policy | Smite Club">
  <style>
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff 0%, #e0f2fe 100%);
      padding: 60px 0;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #7dd3fc;
    }
    
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 36px;
      color: #0a0a1a;
    }
    
    .section {
      padding: 50px 0;
    }
    
    .content {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .content h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #0a0a1a;
      margin: 30px 0 15px;
    }
    
    .content p {
      color: #475569;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    
    .content ul {
      color: #475569;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding-left: 25px;
    }
    
    .content li {
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
  </style>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Refund & Transfer Policy</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Full Refunds</h2>
        <p>Full refunds are available up to 30 days before the event. Contact us at info@smiteclub40k.com with your order number to request a refund.</p>
        
        <h2>Ticket Transfers</h2>
        <p>Can't make it? Transfer your ticket to another player:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Transfers allowed up to 30 days before the event</li>
          <li>For SEO 2026: transfers must be completed by February 1, 2026</li>
          <li>Email info@smiteclub40k.com with both player names</li>
          <li>No fees for transfers</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>No Refunds Within 30 Days</h2>
        <p>Within 30 days of the event, tickets are non-refundable. Transfers may still be possible on a case-by-case basis â€” contact us as soon as you know you can't attend.</p>
        
        <h2>Event Cancellation</h2>
        <p>In the unlikely event that Smite Club cancels an event, full refunds will be issued to all ticket holders within 14 days.</p>
        
        <p style="margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">
          <strong>Questions?</strong> Email <a href="mailto:info@smiteclub40k.com" style="color: #0ea5e9;">info@smiteclub40k.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
